        <h2 class="tac">Portland, Aug 22 - 23</h2>

        <p>Our first event in Portland is also our last time running the Front-End Design Conference. We hope to meet many of the awesome members of the Portland community that we have heard so much about.</p>

        <div class="holy-shit-pay-attention-to-me pam tac mbm">

