          </div>

          <div class="grid-box grid-box--tablet--1of2">

            <h3 class="tac">Meetups</h3>

            <p class="tac">Aug 23, All day</p>

            <p>While learning from the presentations is the focus of conferences, the conversations outside of them are often the best part of the event. They are what lead to friendships, work opportunities, and collaboration.</p>

            <p>Rather than have a second day of presentations, we're hoping to get people from the event together to explore Portland and hang out.</p>

            <p>Details aren't finalized, but we're lining up some creative jam sessions, some hiking/outdoorsy fun, and times for talking shop over the amazing food and drinks in Portland.</p>

          </div>

        </div>

